title: Macau Employed Persons
description: The number of employed persons in Macau decreased to 363 Thousand in the third quarter of 2022 from 364.20 Thousand in the second quarter of 2022. Employed Persons in Macau averaged 298.40 Thousand from 1996 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 401.90 Thousand in the second quarter of 2020 and a record low of 193 Thousand in the third quarter of 1996. In Macau, employed persons are individuals with a minimum required age who work during a certain time for a business. This page provides - Macao Employed Persons - actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Statistics and Census Service, Government of Macao SAR
